Name: Felix Jumpman
About the game: One man strandet in space, Limited air, His space ship in ruins, Now this brave adventure must jump to survive, Now he must become Felix Jumpman. Felix Jumpman is a action based game, were you play as Felix jumpman, who has to jump from comet to comet to collect air tanks and reserve part for his space ship, so how far can you jump ?
